Privacy Policy for Media X



At Media X, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring your personal information is handled securely and responsibly. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your data when you use our application.

1. Information We Collect

Media X may collect the following types of information:

Usage Data: Information about how you interact with the application, such as playback history, preferences, and settings.

Technical Data: Device information, operating system version, and error logs for troubleshooting and improving app performance.

Optional Data: When using features such as URL playback, Media X may process URLs you provide, but we do not store or share this data.


We do not collect personally identifiable information (PII) unless explicitly provided by you (e.g., when contacting support).

2. How We Use Your Information

We use the collected data to:

Enhance app performance and user experience.

Provide customer support and resolve technical issues.

Improve Media X features and functionality based on user behavior and feedback.


3. Data Storage and Security

Your data is processed locally on your device. Media X does not store or transmit your data to external servers unless required for specific features (e.g., streaming from online sources). In such cases, we take reasonable steps to protect your data using encryption and secure protocols.

4. Third-Party Services

Media X may integrate with third-party services (e.g., online streaming platforms) to enable certain features. These services operate under their own privacy policies, and Media X is not responsible for their practices.

5. Your Rights

You have the right to:

Access and manage your app data through settings.

Request deletion of your data by uninstalling the app.

Contact us for any privacy concerns or questions.


6. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in the app or legal requirements. Updates will be posted within the app, and the "Effective Date" will be revised accordingly.



By using Media X, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
